> ask girl about professor

> ask girl about professor
"Wot about the guy at the freak show? Can he be trusted?"

"I don't think so.  I've seen him try to stand up to the clowns when they try to get into the freak show, but he's too old and weak to do anything. Sometimes when the carnival goes too long between...uh...feedings, the clowns sneak into the freak show and eat the pickled punks. It's awful to see."
