> take beanbag

> take beanbag
"So how's about it, sweetcheeks, ready ta test yer skills? Grab that beanbag and give it a little heave!"

You take the beanbag and toss it with all your might at the stack of milk bottles; it bounces right off without any effect.

"Aw, tough break, pal! Looks like ya ain't got what it takes."

